description.narrative: UNICEF Gambia Country Office continued to support and equip the child protection system in the Gambia in 2019 as part of its new Strategic Plan 2017-2021. The GCO supported the review of legislation such as the Children's Act and the Birth deaths and Marriages Act with data collection initiative for vulnerable children through the child protection case management system. GCO supported the institutional strengthening of the MWCSW and its Department of Social Welfare; the Judiciary; the Department of Community Development under MLRG and its purview of the decentralized structures in country. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/12/2019
